Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:39.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! You don't even know\Nyour Zanpaku-to’s name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:43.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And you think you can fight me\Nas an equal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's 2000 years too soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:51.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Zabimaru!\NLook in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What stands before you is…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:56.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,your prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:11.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will lose to Renji Abarai,\Nand die on this spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:29.00,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,BLEACH 17
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:33.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:36.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what's known as\Na difference in strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Zanpaku-to changes\Nin size and shape
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.16,0:02:42.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,depending on its wielder's\Nspiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:46.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the manifestation\Nof my spiritual energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:52.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well kid, I think it's about\Ntime I got going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like the air here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One attack will show him\Nthe difference in strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:01.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,make him realize that\Nhe has no chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:04.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and back down while his wound\Nis not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was my hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:10.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But Ichigo would never give up\Nbecause of such a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:13.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still move, Ichigo? Then run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:21.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:27.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:32.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Rukia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:35.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:40.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to deepen your guilt?!\NLet go, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:41.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:45.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stand! Stand and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:46.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:58.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? You still have\Nthe strength to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:03.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I was just thinking that\Nit's no fun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to finish off someone who\Ncan't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:14.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, fight hard and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:18.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, if you can stand,\Nget away! Run, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:26.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:31.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't attack, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this sudden increase\Nin his Spiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:17.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was about to die earlier!\NWhere'd he get all this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your moves have slowed\Ndown considerably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You just got faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand this,\Nbut it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:32.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even feel\Nthe pain from the wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:35.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't feel like I can lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roar, Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji is being pressured! Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at dodging around!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How much higher can\Nhis spiritual energy go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that's about to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:23.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it in time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:38.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:41.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My Zanpaku-to…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:46.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… he didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:49.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:53.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He can't do a thing from\Nthat distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is he coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:24.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did he get me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even tell if\NI was hit from the back…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:32.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Byakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:57.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been awhile since I saw it,\Nbut he's awesome, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I had to strain to follow\Nhis second attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But his first one…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even tell
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,when he drew his sword,\Nor put it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I couldn't see it coming…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:17.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He probably doesn't even\Nknow what happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:25.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that extraordinary\NSpiritual Pressure he demonstrated earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:36.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No… You didn't need to help me\N with a kid of this level, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:42.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.\NIf all I did was watch each time…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:43.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'd get rusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:48.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, this man is… And I am…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:49.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, Renji! Ichigo is…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:06.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, fool?!\NLook hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:08.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The kid is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:16.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By just touching him, your sentence\Nwill increase by 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:20.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you multiply\Nyour crimes for a dead person?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:26.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one\Nwho got Ichigo involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what's wrong with\Nmy coming to him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So even if it would make\Nyour sentence harsher,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:41.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you can't stay away...\Nfrom this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This kid…looks a lot…\Nlike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:12.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:17.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This kid…looks a lot like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:26.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,"He's dead," you say?\N"Looks a lot like him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:30.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit talking about me\Nlike I'm not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:32.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichi--!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:35.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:40.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you.\NLook at me when you speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:46.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This kid can still move?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:50.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… You don't need that arm, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:54.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:11:00.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What're you doing, Rukia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a human…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you grab\Nmy brother like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:13.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:19.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:23.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Through his actions just now…\NI, Rukia Kuchiki, have opened my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:28.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me back to\Nthe Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:31.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will atone for my sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:35.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait you…!\NWhat're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:41.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know when\Nto give up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:44.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit squirming around and die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:49.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There is no need to inflict\Nthe final blow upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:53.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him and\Nhe will eventually die on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of joke is this?!\NLook at me, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:06.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do not move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:12.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take even one step from there…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:15.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Try to come after me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:18.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll…I'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You will die anyway…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:28.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so stay there and live,\Neven if just one second longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:39.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I will not inflict the finishing blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:44.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With the two attacks just now,\NI've shattered his Soul Chain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:46.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and Hakusui - Soul Sleep,\Nthe vital spots of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:50.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He should die in less than an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:57.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And even if he does survive,\Nhis powers will be lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:02.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reaper power, as well\Nas his spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:04.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:06.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:25.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't speak…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:24.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was protected…again…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:55.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts. My body feels heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.21,0:14:58.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:20.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt.\NOh no, am I about to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.57,0:15:25.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I probably don't feel pain\Nbecause I'm on the verge of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:33.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right… my body was so cold earlier,\Nbut I'm feeling warmth now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:46.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good reaction! That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:52.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Kurosaki is awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you before!\NYou're Hat-and Clogs’ friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:15:58.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you under\Nthe covers with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm not dead?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:12.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And this isn't my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:18.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. You mustn't be up, Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your wounds haven't closed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you move around too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:27.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hat-and-Clogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:32.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So this is your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:33.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So you saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:42.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That tone is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:45.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds as though\Nyou didn't want me to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:55.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah… Ishida was there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:57.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to him?\NIs he here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, he went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:06.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He lost a lot of blood,\Nbut his wounds weren't too serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:09.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he lay there like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he wouldn't have died\Nfor a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:15.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I was able to treat\Nmost of his wounds there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:21.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was worried about you\Nwhen he left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:24.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:29.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to rest here awhile…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.\NBut I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:40.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But rather…\Nplease take care of Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:47.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anyone who can defeat\Nthose guys right now, it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can save Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:54.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...is "him." So he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:02.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What does he expect me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:11.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia has gone back\Nto the Soul Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How do I go after her?!\NHow do I save her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way can I do that…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:27.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:31.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's a way to get to the Soul Society…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:37.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How? How do I get there?!\NTell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:41.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I'll tell you.\NBut there's one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.96,0:18:42.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:47.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. For the next ten days,\Nstudy how to fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:52.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Study?! What?\NYou want me to train?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:56.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia may be executed\Nover there at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:59.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get to\Nthe Soul Society and…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:01.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:02.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:09.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is,\Nif you go there now, you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:17.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you beat them?\NIf you fought with them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:23.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I let you try\Nand fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.07,0:19:28.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I figured you would\Nunderstand that better than words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:31.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With your level of strength now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:35.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you won't be of any good\Nin the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:38.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:44.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A weak person entering the enemy's den…\Nthat's called suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:49.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You want to save Rukia?\NDon't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:52.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use others as a reason\Nfor walking straight into death's arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Society usually
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:04.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,has a one-month waiting period\Nbefore an execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:07.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This holds true in Rukia's case, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Execution?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from the way\Nhumans are executed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.30,0:20:16.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have ten days to bully you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:20.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then seven days to open\Nthe gate to Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:25.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And 13 days after we arrive\Nin Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:28.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We will have lots of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:44.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can I become stronger in ten days?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:49.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly! That is if you truly wish to\Nsave Rukia from the bottom of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.07,0:20:55.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings are stronger than steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:59.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abandon any doubt you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:04.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ten days. Can you play a game\Nof life and death with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:13.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:24.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I felt as though…the rain stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:46.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:48.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:52.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.05,0:21:54.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:56.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.38,0:21:58.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:00.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:05.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:07.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:09.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.98,0:22:12.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:14.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:16.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:18.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.57,0:22:20.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:23.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:26.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.30,0:22:28.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:32.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:34.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:39.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji Abarai shows you the\N"Proper way to use the Zanpaku-to"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:42.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First, you call out the name of\Nyour Zanpaku-to to release its power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:44.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then you slash and swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:46.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Slash, and slash, and slash, and slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:48.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes! That’s not explaining anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:49.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do the preview!